    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Enough!  You have soiled my fields for long enough!  It is time to *purify* you!",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 3000
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 1,
      "ResponsesCount": 1,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 1
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "By the nine HELLS!  Have you come to destroy my home as well?!",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 3001
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 2,
      "ResponsesCount": 4,
      "TriggerIndex": 1,
      "Index": 2
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "You are mortals passing through my home, that is enough for me to kill you!",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24597
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 6,
      "ResponsesCount": 2,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 3
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "The need definitely *calls!*  We always hunger for fresh flesh, and there isn't enough of this little cleric here to satiate all of us... DIIEEE!",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 26843
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 8,
      "ResponsesCount": 1,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 4
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "How amusing!  That fool Kratuuk is so easily manipulated.  I will relish in feeding upon your flesh, and afterwards, I shall eliminate Kratuuk and his worthless minions once and for all.  I will show Saablic Tan that I am enough to guard the Fields of Slaughter!",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
